.TH RIGD 8 "8 September 2023" "rig-control"
.
.SH NAME
rigd
.
.SH DESCRIPTION
.
.IR rigd (8)
is a daemon to control amateur radio transceivers.
.IR rigd (8)
listens for incoming TCP/IP connections from rig-control compatible clients.
.
.
